message.skylands.help.4: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% home <player> <r>→ Teleport to an Island you are member of.
message.skylands.help.5: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% members invite <player> <r>→ Invite player to your Island.
message.skylands.help.6: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% members remove <player> <r>→ Remove player from your Island.
message.skylands.help.7: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% accept <player> <r>→ Accept Island join invite request.
message.skylands.help.8: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% kick <player> <r>→ Kick player from your Island.
message.skylands.help.9: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% ban <player> <r>→ Ban player from visiting your Island.
message.skylands.help.10: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% unban <player> <r>→ Unban player to allow visiting your Island.
message.skylands.help.12: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% settings <r>→ Opens the island settings menu.
message.skylands.help.15: - <color:#98f9ff>/%prefix% settings toggle-visits <r>→ Enables/disables ability to visit your Island.
